            <div class="title">
                Housing Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1952-04-22/debates/e8764252-73a3-4683-a8fe-199db4fa82c7/HousingMoney" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
