<p class="">Does the hon. Gentleman consider the Dudley Committee standard a mockery standard?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7046375d-4e79-42ac-b44f-43700256de32" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
