            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eba249e4-100a-49b3-9e9b-86d42e3f42ff" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
