            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-498b2fc0-920d-42b3-8162-cb56bd87fdb6">
                The Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministry of Housing and Local Government (Mr. Ernest Marples)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-498b2fc0-920d-42b3-8162-cb56bd87fdb6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
