                Mr. Gibson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1faf9a72-218c-41de-92d7-9511b2c4fb71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
