            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-442a24ef-2bf7-408d-b845-4b7a619eab96">
                Mr. E. G. Gooch  (Norfolk, North)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-442a24ef-2bf7-408d-b845-4b7a619eab96" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
