    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My hon. and learned Friend says, "A Labour councillor," all councils are being won by Labour now. Any scheme should satisfy other conditions, such as whether the owner should dispose of the property and the council buy it back again at about 5 per cent. per annum, plus improvements at valuation, and that the purchaser should keep it in a state of repair comparable to that at which it has been kept. I do not know what would be done in Cardiff, where they spend nothing on repairs at all.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
