                Mr. Pannell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-41c14e03-6abe-4e55-9a44-fa73ad4672f2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
