    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. and learned Gentleman said that there is no difference if the council lend the money. Would he not agree that the mere acquisition of a house, the ownership of a house, gives the occupier a greater interest in it and, other things being equal, is calculated to produce a superior type of citizen?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-59743ca5-2be5-4017-8b8e-050529d686a5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
