<p class="">I was referring to Clause 2.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-fe534505-b401-44a9-96ab-73bb31a43f3c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-22/debates/205018f0-a846-4818-90cd-0ab27d528229/HousingBill#contribution-fe534505-b401-44a9-96ab-73bb31a43f3c">
